---
// TODO(sandeep): Hand-edit this copy. Cut anything that still reads as
// AI-generated or non-relatable. Make it yours - specific, odd, true.
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import { SOCIAL } from "../config";
import profile from "../assets/profile.png";
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="A software engineer in Seattle. A little about me, beyond the resume."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Nice to <em>meet</em> you</h1>
  </section>

  <h2 class="sr-only">About</h2>

  <figure class="portrait">
    <Picture
      src={profile}
      alt="Sandeep Danda"
      widths={[320, 480, 640, 960]}
      sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 38rem"
      formats={["avif", "webp"]}
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </figure>

  <div class="bio">
    <p>
      I write backends. The part I like is the shape of the thing -
      idempotent writes, replay queues, alarms that fire for the right
      reason. Less glamorous than it sounds, more interesting than it
      looks.
    </p>
    <p>
      I grew up in Thorrur, a small town in Telangana, and then in
      Hyderabad. My first real job was at Nucleus Software in Delhi
      writing Java for a bank's loan processing module, which is also
      where I had my first real production outage. Then Deloitte, doing
      Salesforce admin and Apex work. After that I came to the US for my
      masters at the University at Buffalo, and eventually ended up in
      Seattle.
    </p>
    <p>
      Lately I have been pulled into AI tooling - agents, MCPs, skills,
      configs, and the slightly obsessive fun of making a team's tools
      do more than they were designed for. If I had to pick the career
      again I would still pick engineering, but this time for the
      curiosity, not the path.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work: cooking, badminton, cricket, and since I moved
      to Seattle, hiking. My favorite movies are Shawshank Redemption
      and Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi - one for patience, the other for the
      quiet kind of love. I like kindness, people who are a little
      different, and the missing pieces in a thing more than the
      finished ones.
    </p>
    <p>
      Grateful to God, to my parents, and to a life that let me learn
      all of that.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="links-section">
    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p class="intro">
      I read most things that land in my inbox. Email is the fastest way.
    </p>

    <ul class="contacts">
      <li>
        <a href={SOCIAL.email}>
          <svg class="icon" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/>
            <path d="m22 7-10 5L2 7"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="method">Email</span>
          <span class="handle">sandeepdanda.dev@gmail.com</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href={SOCIAL.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="icon" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M20.45 20.45h-3.56v-5.57c0-1.33-.03-3.04-1.85-3.04-1.85 0-2.13 1.44-2.13 2.94v5.67H9.35V9h3.42v1.56h.05c.48-.9 1.64-1.85 3.38-1.85 3.61 0 4.28 2.37 4.28 5.46v6.28zM5.34 7.43a2.06 2.06 0 1 1 0-4.12 2.06 2.06 0 0 1 0 4.12zm1.78 13.02H3.56V9h3.56v11.45zM22.22 0H1.77C.79 0 0 .77 0 1.72v20.56C0 23.23.79 24 1.77 24h20.45c.98 0 1.78-.77 1.78-1.72V1.72C24 .77 23.2 0 22.22 0z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="method">LinkedIn</span>
          <span class="handle">@sandeepsde</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href={SOCIAL.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="icon" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 0c-6.63 0-12 5.37-12 12 0 5.3 3.44 9.8 8.21 11.39.6.11.82-.26.82-.58 0-.29-.01-1.05-.02-2.06-3.34.72-4.04-1.61-4.04-1.61-.55-1.39-1.34-1.76-1.34-1.76-1.09-.74.08-.73.08-.73 1.21.09 1.85 1.24 1.85 1.24 1.07 1.84 2.81 1.31 3.5 1 .11-.78.42-1.31.76-1.61-2.67-.3-5.47-1.33-5.47-5.94 0-1.31.47-2.38 1.24-3.22-.12-.3-.54-1.52.12-3.17 0 0 1.01-.32 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.4 3-.4 1.02 0 2.05.14 3 .4 2.29-1.55 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.87.12 3.17.77.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.62-2.81 5.63-5.48 5.93.43.37.82 1.1.82 2.22 0 1.61-.02 2.9-.02 3.3 0 .32.22.69.83.57C20.57 21.8 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="method">GitHub</span>
          <span class="handle">@sandeepdanda</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    margin: 0 0 4rem 0;
  }
  .kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 0;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .bio {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .bio p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }
  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .portrait {
    margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }
  .portrait img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 4px;
    filter: grayscale(0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }

  .links-section {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .links-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }
  .intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .contacts {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .contacts li a {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 28px 6rem 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0.5rem 1rem 0.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: padding-left 200ms ease-out, color 150ms ease-out;
  }
  .contacts li:first-child a { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .contacts li a:hover {
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .contacts li a:hover .icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  .icon {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    max-width: 22px;
    max-height: 22px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    transition: color 150ms ease-out, transform 200ms ease-out;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: block;
  }
  .method {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .handle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: inherit;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .contacts li a {
      grid-template-columns: 24px 1fr;
      gap: 0.875rem;
    }
    .method { display: none; }
  }
</style>
